o believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.331948, "shard": "06", "shelf_id": "sn99063957, 1910-11-29, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/oru", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["oregon", "united states", "marion", "salem", "newspapers", "salem (or.)"], "subject_headings": ["Salem (Or.)--Newspapers", "Oregon--Salem", "United States--Oregon--Marion--Salem"], "subjects": [{"marion": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:marion&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"oregon": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:oregon&fo=json"}, {"salem": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:salem&fo=json"}, {"salem (or.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:salem+%28or.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-07-15T15:32:38.169Z", "title": "Daily capital journal (Salem, Oregon), November 29, 1910", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn99063957/1910-11-29/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn99063957/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn99063957", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/5a93bb22-17bd-5cd9-8bab-f1d537edd46b"], "batch": ["oru_ashland_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1903", "description": ["Daily (except Sunday) Vol. 13, no. 272 (Nov. 25, 1903)-42nd year, no. 250 (Oct. 22, 1919). Also issued on microfilm from University of Oregon. Archived issues are available in digital format as part of the Historic Oregon Newspaper online collection. Archived issues are available in digital format as part of the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Capital journal (Salem, Or. : 1919) 2470-6779 (DLC)sn 90066132 (OCoLC)21019600"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.942Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-01", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-01"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn99063957/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [44.939016, -123.039307], "location": ["oregon", "marion", "salem", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-123.039307, 44.939016], "number": ["42946548", "univ of oregon libr", "sn99063956", "microfilm service copy", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn99063957/1919-10-22/ed-1/", "2024-06-05t12:26:16.235228", "sn90066132", "sn99063957", "online resource", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2025-11-07t12:30:21.100000", "microfilm master", "2163-8535", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn99063957/1903-11-25/ed-1/", "4967", "1"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Capital journal", "Daily journal"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "catalog", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "daily capital journal (salem, oregon) 1903-1